      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s ready for your next big adventure? I\u2019m parting with this beauty, and she has been so well-loved! It runs like a total dream and is in wonderful shape, making it the perfect choice if you want a quality car without that brand-new price tag. It's super clean and ready to hit the road today\u2014come take it for a spin and see for yourself, you\u2019re going to love it!",
