    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically robust 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the legendary S54B32 3.2L inline-six. This high-revving powerplant delivers linear throttle response through six individual throttle bodies and is mated to a desirable 6-speed Getrag manual transmission. The chassis dynamics are sharp, benefiting from a documented rear subframe reinforcement and a refreshed suspension setup. The variable M differential lock provides exceptional traction and corner-exit stability. Recent comprehensive maintenance includes a full VANOS overhaul and precision valve adjustment, ensuring the valvetrain performs to factory specifications. While the exterior shows minor signs of honest road use, the drivetrain and structural integrity remain excellent, offering the visceral, analog driving experience this platform is celebrated for.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
