    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained sedan offers the perfect balance of performance and everyday comfort. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, though upon close inspection, you will find a few minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small scuff on the rear passenger wheel\u2014typical signs of careful use that do not detract from its overall sharp appearance. Inside, the cabin remains a smoke-free sanctuary; the premium leather upholstery is supple, showing only light creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster. All interior electronics, including the navigation system and dual-zone climate control, function perfectly. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health with a consistent service history; the engine pulls strongly, and the transmission shifts seamlessly. We have recently completed a full multi-point inspection and a fresh oil change, ensuring the car is ready for the road immediately. If you are looking for a reliable, high-quality vehicle that has been treated with respect, this is an outstanding choice.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
