    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my absolute favorite ride and it\u2019s been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super well-taken care of over the years\u2014perfect for someone looking for a reliable daily driver that still turns heads! I\u2019ve loved every mile in it, but it\u2019s finally time for it to find a new home. It runs great and is ready to hit the road today. Feel free to reach out with any questions at all\u2014I\u2019d love to see it go to someone who will appreciate it as much as I have!",
